      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single device specimen acceptable.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond single-specimen testing is not required at MRL 2. One physical pump specimen was used for all validation experiments, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Level 1 achieved."
