    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD model is fit for the intended COU based on the overall weight of evidence. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; the majority meet or exceed required levels. Shortfalls in discretization error, test conditions, and model form were noted in internal review minutes but were judged by the team to be compensated by the strong output comparison results and the conservative 20% acceptance band. The decision is recorded as Accepted. No formal compensating controls or residual risk justification documents were appended to this record.",
